    <entry>
      <title>X-Blog 快速入门</title>
      <link href="/2099/12/31/default-quickstart/"/>
      <url>/2099/12/31/default-quickstart/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>[置顶] X-Blog 是一个基于 Hexo + Butterfly 搭建的个人博客站点；Hexo 是一个快速、简单且强大的博客框架，它使用 Markdown 来编写内容，并生成静态网页。本篇文章主要讲述 X-Blog 的基本使用</p><blockquote><p>温馨提示：如果您当前的屏幕分辨率超出了 1920 x 1080，建议将浏览器窗口缩放为 125%</p><p>快捷键：Ctrl + 鼠标滚轮</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="环境搭建">环境搭建</h2><h3 id="安装">安装</h3><p>本教程不再展开去讲从零开始搭建博客，因为在官网已经有很详细的说明，参见如下</p><ul><li>Hexo：<a href="https://hexo.io/">https://hexo.io/</a></li><li>Butterfly：<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/">https://butterfly.js.org/</a></li></ul><p>以下列出部分安装命令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-theme-butterfly</span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果安装的是最新版本，可能会出现不稳定或版本冲突的情况（例如使用 <code>npm</code> 安装某个依赖包报 <code>err</code>）。以下展示本博客用的所有相关依赖版本，更新于 <code>2024.11.20</code> 之前，如有需要，可以通过 <code>npm install [package]@[version]</code> 的形式来指定安装的版本号 （Node.js 中文网：<a href="https://nodejs.p2hp.com/%EF%BC%89">https://nodejs.p2hp.com/）</a></p><p>主依赖</p><table><thead><tr><th>名称</th><th>版本</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>npm</code></td><td><code>10.9.0</code></td><td>包管理工具</td></tr><tr><td><code>hexo-cli</code></td><td><code>4.3.2</code></td><td><code>hexo</code> 命令行执行</td></tr><tr><td><code>Hexo</code></td><td><code>7.3.0</code></td><td>博客基础框架</td></tr><tr><td><code>Butterfly</code></td><td><code>5.2.0</code></td><td>主题风格</td></tr></tbody></table><p>其他依赖项可以参考 <code>package.json</code></p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;dependencies&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^7.3.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-deployer-git&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^4.0.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-generator-archive&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^2.0.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-generator-category&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^2.0.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-generator-index&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^4.0.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-generator-search&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^2.4.3&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-generator-tag&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^2.0.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-renderer-ejs&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^2.0.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-renderer-markdown-it&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^7.1.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-renderer-pug&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^3.0.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-renderer-stylus&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^3.0.1&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-server&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^3.0.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-theme-landscape&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^1.0.0&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;hexo-wordcount&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^6.0.1&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;markdown-it-emoji&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;^3.0.0&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="部署到-GitHub-Page">部署到 GitHub Page</h3><p>GitHub Pages 是 GitHub 提供的一项静态站点托管服务，它允许用户直接从 GitHub 上的仓库获取 HTML、CSS 和 JavaScript 文件，然后发布网站。将您的项目部署到 GitHub Page，让您随时随地都能阅览文章</p><h4 id="第一步、新建一个仓库">第一步、新建一个仓库</h4><p>进入 GitHub 创建仓库的页面</p><p>仓库名称需要填写 <code>[username].github.io</code>，这是 GitHub Page 的固定格式，将 <code>[username]</code> 替换成自己账号的用户名</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/0.png" alt=""></p><p>填写完成后，点击下面的 <code>Create repository</code> 按钮完成创建</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/1.png" alt=""></p><h4 id="第二步、设置个人访问令牌">第二步、设置个人访问令牌</h4><p>个人访问令牌 (Personal Access Token, PAT) 是 GitHub 提供的一种身份验证方式，主要用于增强账户的安全性，并允许用户通过 API 或命令行工具与 GitHub 进行交互</p><p>进入用户设置页面</p><p>点击左侧菜单底部的 <code>Developer settings</code> 按钮</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/2.png" alt=""></p><p>点击 <code>Tokens (classic)</code> 按钮，再点击 <code>Generate new token (classic)</code> 按钮，进入 Token 的编辑页面</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/3.png" alt=""></p><p>Note 输入框填写这个 Token 的用途；Expiration 选择到期时间，图中的示例是永不到期</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/4.png" alt=""></p><p><code>Select scopes</code> 根据自己实际需求，选择允许在哪些作用域下访问个人令牌，图中的示例是全选</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/5.png" alt=""></p><p>最后，点击下面的 <code>Generate token</code> 按钮来生成 Token</p><p>需要将最终生成的 Token 保存到本地，用于项目推送</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/6.png" alt=""></p><h4 id="第三步、创建-SSH-Key">第三步、创建 SSH Key</h4><p>GitHub SSH Key 是用于通过 SSH 协议与 GitHub 进行安全通信的一种身份验证方式。SSH (Secure Shell) 是一种加密的网络协议，用于在不安全的网络中安全地进行远程登录和文件传输</p><p>终端输入 <code>ssh-keygen -t rsa</code> 命令后 Enter 来创建 SSH Key</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; ssh-keygen -t rsa</span><br><span class="line">Generating public/private rsa key pair.</span><br><span class="line">Enter file <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">which</span> to save the key (C:\Users\lphce/.ssh/id_rsa):</span><br><span class="line">Enter passphrase (empty <span class="keyword">for</span> no passphrase):</span><br><span class="line">Enter same passphrase again:</span><br><span class="line">Your identification has been saved <span class="keyword">in</span> C:\Users\lphce/.ssh/id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">Your public key has been saved <span class="keyword">in</span> C:\Users\lphce/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br><span class="line">The key fingerprint is:</span><br><span class="line">SHA256:RAsKYaBXkGcE7DIzj0Z/dxXtgCFABgKXFYt7VSsLOys lphce@XYZ</span><br><span class="line">The key<span class="string">&#x27;s randomart image is:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">+---[RSA 3072]----+</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|o.o==+*   .      |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|+.oo * = o o     |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|+ B = * o * .    |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|.o X = = + +     |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|o * = + S . .    |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">| = = . . o       |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|E o     .        |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|                 |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">|                 |</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">+----[SHA256]-----+</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行成功后，会在 <code>C:\Users\[username]\.ssh</code> 生成 <code>id_rsa.pub</code></p><p>进入 GitHub 用户设置页面</p><p>点击左侧菜单 <code>SSH and GPG keys</code> 按钮，再点击 <code>New SSH key</code> 按钮</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/7.png" alt=""></p><p>进入 SSH Key 编辑页面，将 <code>id_rsa.pub</code> 内容复制到 Key 文本域</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/8.png" alt=""></p><p>最后点击 <code>Add SSH key</code> 按钮完成创建</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/9.png" alt=""></p><h4 id="第四步、推送到远端">第四步、推送到远端</h4><p>在项目下执行 <code>hexo d</code></p><p>首次推送，会出现登录提示</p><p><img src="/post_media/default-quickstart/10.png" alt=""></p><p>输入您的 GitHub 账号和密码，点击 Login 按钮</p><p>在终端输入用户名和 PAT，Enter</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Logon failed, use ctrl+c to cancel basic credential prompt.</span><br><span class="line">Username <span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="string">&#x27;https://github.com&#x27;</span>: lphcev</span><br><span class="line">Password <span class="keyword">for</span> <span class="string">&#x27;https://lphcev@github.com&#x27;</span>:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>再次强调，Password for ‘<a href="https://lphcev@github.com">https://lphcev@github.com</a>’: 这段不是输入 GitHub 密码，而是个人访问令牌的 Value</p></blockquote><p>当终端出现如下信息，代表已经推送成功</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">remote: Resolving deltas: 100% (10/10), done.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>经过了上述一系列配置，之后的每次推送只需在项目下执行 <code>hexo d</code> 即可完成，无需额外输入用户认证信息</p><h2 id="Hexo-常用命令">Hexo 常用命令</h2><p><code>hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</code></p><p>创建命令，<code>layout</code> 指定布局，<code>title</code> 指定主标题。可以简写成 <code>hexo n</code></p><p><code>hexo clean</code></p><p>用于清理缓存文件，即删除 <code>public</code> 文件夹。</p><p><code>hexo generate</code></p><p>用于生成静态文件，执行后在 Hexo 站点根目录下生成 <code>public</code> 文件夹。可以简写成 <code>hexo g</code></p><p><code>hexo deploy</code></p><p>用于部署项目。可以简写成 <code>hexo d</code></p><p><code>hexo server</code></p><p>用于启动本地服务器，默认端口为 <code>4000</code>。可以简写成 <code>hexo s</code></p><h3 id="关于-layout">关于 layout</h3><p>在创建时，<code>layout</code> 是可选参数，用于指定布局，常用布局有以下两种</p><ul><li><code>post</code> 创建普通的博客文章。它通常包含标题、日期、分类、标签、摘要和正文等部分</li><li><code>page</code> 创建页面，如关于页面、联系页面等。页面与文章的主要区别在于它们在网站结构中的位置和用途。页面通常不包含在博客文章的列表中，而是作为网站的独立部分存在</li></ul><h2 id="Markdown">Markdown</h2><p>Markdown 是一种轻量级标记语言，允许使用简单的文本格式来编写具备特定排版格式的文档。Markdown 的核心理念是“重内容轻形式”，即让写作者能够专注于内容本身，而无需过多纠结于排版细节。它通过简单的标记语法，使普通文本内容具有一定的格式，从而提升了工作效率</p><h3 id="语法规则">语法规则</h3><p>Markdown 的语法规则相对简单且直观，主要包括以下元素</p><h4 id="标题">标题</h4><p>通过在单词或短语前面添加井号 <code>#</code> 来创建，<code>#</code> 的数量代表了标题的级别。通常，一级标题用于整篇文章的标题（但很多文章选择省略一级标题，直接使用二级标题作为根标题），后续标题等级依次递减，用于文章内部的小节划分</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级标题</span><br><span class="line">## 二级标题</span><br><span class="line">### 三级标题</span><br><span class="line">#### 四级标题</span><br><span class="line">##### 五级标题</span><br><span class="line">###### 六级标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="列表">列表</h4><p>无序列表通过在每个列表项前面添加破折号 <code>-</code>、星号 <code>*</code> 或加号 <code>+</code> 来创建</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">- 列表项 1</span><br><span class="line">- 列表项 2</span><br><span class="line">- 列表项 3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* 列表项 4</span><br><span class="line">* 列表项 5</span><br><span class="line">* 列表项 6</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">+ 列表项 7</span><br><span class="line">+ 列表项 8</span><br><span class="line">+ 列表项 9</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有序列表则在每个列表项前添加数字并紧跟一个句点</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. 列表项 A</span><br><span class="line">2. 列表项 B</span><br><span class="line">3. 列表项 C</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="超链接和图片">超链接和图片</h4><p>通过特定的语法来插入网页链接和图片</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![图片描述](图片网址)</span><br><span class="line">[链接描述](链接网址)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>“图片描述”相当于注释，不会在网页中显示，“链接描述”是用户点击后跳转到的目标地址的文本描述</p><h4 id="引用">引用</h4><p>使用符号 <code>&gt;</code> 来实现，可以单独划出一块编辑空间，与正文形成明显的划分。引用块内部可以嵌套其他 Markdown 元素，如标题、列表、代码等。在引用块内部再次使用 <code>&gt;</code> 符号进行嵌套引用，每嵌套一层，<code>&gt;</code> 符号数量增加</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt; 这是一段测试内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="代码">代码</h4><p>使用反引号 (`) 将代码内容包裹起来，或使用三个反引号 (```) 包围代码块，并可指定编程语言以获得合适的高亮</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是行内代码：`console.log(&quot;Hello World&quot;)`</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是代码块</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```js</span><br><span class="line">function fn() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    console.log(&quot;Hello World&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="文本强调">文本强调</h4><p>使用星号 <code>*</code> 或下划线 <code>_</code> 将文本设置为粗体或斜体来强调其重要性</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*这是一段斜体内容*</span><br><span class="line">_这是一段斜体内容_</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">**这是一段粗体内容**</span><br><span class="line">__这是一段粗体内容__</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">***这是一段加粗且倾斜的内容***</span><br><span class="line">___这是一段加粗且倾斜的内容___</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="分隔符">分隔符</h4><p>单独一行上使用三个或多个星号 <code>***</code>、破折号 <code>---</code> 或下划线 <code>___</code> 来创建分隔线</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">***</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">___</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="表格">表格</h4><p>使用三个或多个连字符 <code>---</code> 分割标题行和内容行，并使用管道 <code>|</code> 分隔每列</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| A1 | A2 | A3 |</span><br><span class="line">| -- | -- | -- |</span><br><span class="line">| B1 | B2 | B3 |</span><br><span class="line">| C1 | C2 | C3 |</span><br><span class="line">| D1 | D2 | D3 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="标签外挂">标签外挂</h2><p>在 Hexo 中，标签插件（或称为外挂）是用于增强站点功能的重要组件。这些插件可以添加新的功能、改进现有的功能或与第三方服务集成，接下来介绍几种项目中常用的标签外挂</p><h3 id="Tabs">Tabs</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% tabs example %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab One --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">第一个 Tab</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab Two --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">第二个 Tab</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab Three --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">第三个 Tab</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endtabs %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下</p><div class="tabs"><div class="nav-tabs"><button type="button" class="tab active">One</button><button type="button" class="tab">Two</button><button type="button" class="tab">Three</button></div><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content active"><p>第一个 Tab</p></div><div class="tab-item-content"><p>第二个 Tab</p></div><div class="tab-item-content"><p>第三个 Tab</p></div></div><div class="tab-to-top"><button type="button" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div><h2 id="Mermaid-示例">Mermaid 示例</h2><pre><code class="highlight mermaid">graph TD;  A--&gt;B;  B--&gt;C;  B--&gt;D</code></pre><div class="mermaid-wrap"><pre class="mermaid-src" hidden>  pietitle Language&quot;Java&quot; : 30&quot;HTML&quot; : 10&quot;CSS&quot; : 20&quot;JavaScript&quot; : 50  </pre></div>]]></content>
      
      
