      <title>Express 笔记</title>
      <link href="/2019/08/07/default-express/"/>
      <url>/2019/08/07/default-express/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.expressjs.com.cn/">Express</a> 是基于 Node.js 平台，快速、开放、极简的 Web 开发框架</p><hr><h2 id="快速入门">快速入门</h2><p>依赖安装</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install express --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编写如下 JS 代码，即可创建最简单的 Express 应用程序</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> express = <span class="built_in">require</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;express&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> app = <span class="title function_">express</span>()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> port = <span class="number">3000</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">app.<span class="title function_">get</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span>, <span class="function">(<span class="params">req, res</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    res.<span class="title function_">send</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;Hello World&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">app.<span class="title function_">listen</span>(port, <span class="function">() =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">`Example app listening on port <span class="subst">$&#123;port&#125;</span>`</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此应用程序启动服务器并在端口 3000 上侦听连接。对于对根URL <code>/</code> 或路由的请求，应用程序会以 <code>Hello World</code> 作为响应。对于其他每条路径，它将返回 404 Not Found</p><h2 id="Express-项目生成器">Express 项目生成器</h2><p>需要创建和启动一个完整的 Express 工程，需要使用 <code>express-generator</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npx express-generator</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br><span class="line">npm start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动后，访问 <code>http://localhost:3000/</code> 会跳转到 <code>Welcome to Express</code> 的页面</p><h2 id="基本使用">基本使用</h2><h3 id="路由">路由</h3><p>路由是指确定应用程序如何响应对特定端点的客户端请求，该端点是 URI（或路径）和特定的 HTTP 请求方法 <code>GET/POST</code> 等</p><p>每个路由可以有一个或多个处理程序函数，这些函数在路由匹配时执行</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Listening GET requests</span></span><br><span class="line">app.<span class="title function_">get</span>()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Listening POST requests</span></span><br><span class="line">app.<span class="title function_">post</span>()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Listening PUT requests</span></span><br><span class="line">app.<span class="title function_">put</span>()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Listening DELETE requests</span></span><br><span class="line">app.<span class="title function_">delete</span>()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="获取请求参数">获取请求参数</h3><p>通过 <code>query</code> 属性获取 URL 的查询参数</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">app.<span class="title function_">get</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;/example&#x27;</span>, <span class="function">(<span class="params">req, res</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(req.<span class="property">query</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>访问 <code>http://localhost:3000/example?name=XYZ&amp;age=520</code> 控制台打印结果如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123; name: &#x27;XYZ&#x27;, age: &#x27;520&#x27; &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还可以通过 <code>params</code> 属性获取 URL 的路径参数</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">app.<span class="title function_">get</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;/example/:id&#x27;</span>, <span class="function">(<span class="params">req, res</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(req.<span class="property">params</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>访问 <code>http://localhost:3000/example/520</code> 控制台打印结果如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123; id: &#x27;520&#x27; &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="托管静态文件">托管静态文件</h3><p>为了提供诸如图像、CSS 文件和 JavaScript 文件之类的静态文件，请使用 Express 中的 <code>static</code> 内置中间件函数</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">app.<span class="title function_">use</span>(express.<span class="title function_">static</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;public&#x27;</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/post_media/default-express/0.png" alt=""></p><p>请注意：<code>static</code> 函数需要放在路由处理函数之前执行</p>]]></content>
      
      
